%section.bg-gray-100
  .container.pt-24.px-6.mx-auto.border-t-2
    .pb-32.text-gray-800.text-center
      %h2.text-3xl.font-bold.mb-20 Why Enough Email?
      .grid.md:gap-x-12.grid-cols-1.lg:grid-cols-3
        .mb-14.lg:mb-0
          .rounded-lg.shadow-lg.h-full.block.bg-white
            .flex.justify-center
              .p-4.bg-indigo-600.rounded-full.shadow-lg.inline-block.-mt-8
                = inline_svg_tag "fa-icons/solid/eye-slash.svg", class: "w-8 h-8 text-white fill-current"
            .p-6
              %h5.text-lg.font-semibold.mb-4 No peeking
              %p
                Enough Email works by creating Gmail filters for your entire organization. This means it does not need access to anyone's inbox.
        .mb-14.lg:mb-0
          .rounded-lg.shadow-lg.h-full.block.bg-white
            .flex.justify-center
              .p-4.bg-indigo-600.rounded-full.shadow-lg.inline-block.-mt-8
                = inline_svg_tag "fa-icons/solid/paper-plane.svg", class: "w-8 h-8 text-white fill-current"
            .p-6
              %h5.text-lg.font-semibold.mb-4 Extremely simple UI
              %p
                No software to install, no website to log in to. Forward an unwanted email sample to one of our filter inboxes to set up filters that protect <b>everyone</b> in your organisation.

        .mb-14.lg:mb-0
          .rounded-lg.shadow-lg.h-full.block.bg-white
            .flex.justify-center
              .p-4.bg-indigo-600.rounded-full.shadow-lg.inline-block.-mt-8
                = inline_svg_tag "fa-icons/solid/envelope-circle-check.svg", class: "w-8 h-8 text-white fill-current"
            .p-6
              %h5.text-lg.font-semibold.mb-4 Keep your setup
              %p
                Everyone can keep using their favourite email app - Gmail, Outlook, Mail for iPhone, Superhuman - you name it.

